<h1>Articles</h1>


Our blog has <b><%= Article.public_count %></b> public articles, <b><%= Article.private_count %></b> private articles, <b><%= Article.archived_count %></b> archived articles  and counting!<br>



<ul> 
<% @articles.each do |article| %> 
<% unless article.archived? %>

    <li> 
        <%= link_to article.title, article %>
    </li>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
</ul>
<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>